@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName WenQuanYi Micro Hei
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam maxmessagesize 140
skinparam ParticipantPadding 30
skinparam BoxPadding 8

title 企业RAG — 管理员操作流程（已登录）

actor 管理员 as Admin
participant "Vue 3 前端\n(管理后台)" as Browser
participant "AdminController" as Ctrl
participant "UserService\n(用户与组织标签)" as UserSvc
participant "DocumentService\n(文档管理)" as DocSvc
participant "UsageDashboardService\n(Token 用量统计)" as DashSvc
participant "UserTokenService\n(Token 充值审计)" as TokenSvc
participant "ModelProvider\nConfigService" as ModelSvc
participant "ConversationService\n(对话历史)" as ConvSvc
database "MySQL\n(users / org_tags /\nmodel_config /\ntoken_record)" as DB
database "Redis\n(配额 / 缓存)" as Redis
collections "ES + MinIO" as Ext
collections "Kafka\n(异步向量化队列)" as Kafka

== 1. 用户与组织标签管理 ==

Admin -> Browser: 访问用户管理页面
Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/admin/users/list\n?keyword=&orgTag=&page=&size=
Ctrl -> UserSvc: getPaginatedUserList(...)
UserSvc -> DB: 分页查询 users 表
UserSvc --> Ctrl: Page<UserDTO> (含 orgTags, role)
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200, data:{content:[...], totalElements: N}}

Admin -> Browser: 分配 / 修改用户组织标签
Browser -> Ctrl: PUT /api/v1/admin/users/{userId}/org-tags\n{orgTags: ["tag1", "tag2"]}
Ctrl -> UserSvc: assignOrgTagsToUser(userId, tags)
UserSvc -> DB: UPDATE users SET org_tags = ?
UserSvc -> Redis: OrgTagCacheService\n刷新组织标签子树缓存
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}
Browser --> Admin: 提示更新成功

Admin -> Browser: 管理组织标签树
Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/admin/org-tags/tree
Ctrl -> UserSvc: getOrganizationTagTree()
UserSvc -> DB: 查询全量 org_tags，构建树
Ctrl --> Browser: 层级组织标签树
Browser -> Ctrl: POST|PUT|DELETE /api/v1/admin/org-tags\n{tagId, name, parentTag, uploadMaxSizeMb}
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}

== 2. 模型 Provider 配置 ==

Admin -> Browser: 进入模型配置页
Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/admin/model-providers
Ctrl -> ModelSvc: getCurrentSettings()
ModelSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM model_provider_configs\nWHERE active=true (by scope)
DB --> ModelSvc: llm: DeepSeek/Qwen/ZhipuAI\nembedding: DashScope/Zhipu
Ctrl --> Browser: 当前配置 (API Key 脱敏)

Admin -> Browser: 编辑某 scope 配置
Browser -> Ctrl: PUT /api/v1/admin/model-providers/{scope}\n{providers: [{provider, model, apiBaseUrl, apiKey, active}]}
Ctrl -> ModelSvc: updateScope(scope, request)
ModelSvc -> ModelSvc: SecretCryptoService.encrypt(apiKey)\n→ 密文存储
ModelSvc -> DB: UPSERT model_provider_configs\nSET active=true (唯一)
ModelSvc --> Ctrl: 配置已生效 (即时切换)
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}

Admin -> Browser: 测试模型连接
Browser -> Ctrl: POST /api/v1/admin/model-providers/{scope}/test\n{apiBaseUrl, apiKey, model}
Ctrl -> ModelSvc: testConnection(scope, request)\n(发送最小化聊天请求)
ModelSvc --> Ctrl: {success, latencyMs, errorMsg}
Ctrl --> Browser: 测试结果

== 3. Token 用量统计与充值 ==

Admin -> Browser: 访问 Token 用量仪表盘\n(/token-statistics)
Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/admin/usage/overview?days=7
Ctrl -> DashSvc: buildOverview(days)
DashSvc -> DB: 查询全部用户列表 (userRepository.findAll)
DashSvc -> Redis: 批量读取每日配额计数\n(quota:llm / quota:embedding)
DashSvc -> DashSvc: 计算: 今日用量, 7/30天趋势,\nTop-5 LLM 排名, Top-5 Embedding 排名,\n用量告警 (超 80% 阈值)
DashSvc --> Ctrl: UsageOverview
Ctrl --> Browser: 今日用量 + 趋势 + 排行 + 告警
Browser --> Admin: 多部门、多时间维度\nLLM / Embedding 拆分展示

Admin -> Browser: 为某用户追加 Token
Browser -> Ctrl: POST /api/v1/admin/users/{userId}/tokens/add\n{llmToken, embeddingToken, reason}
Ctrl -> TokenSvc: addLlmTokens / addEmbeddingTokens
TokenSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO user_token_record\n(userId, tokenType, changeType=INCREASE,\namount, balanceBefore, balanceAfter,\nreason, remark="admin={username}")
TokenSvc -> Redis: INCR user:token:llm:{userId}\nINCR user:token:embedding:{userId}
TokenSvc --> Ctrl: 充值成功
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200, data:{usage:{llmUsed, llmBalance, embeddingUsed, embeddingBalance}}}
Browser --> Admin: 新余额已生效

== 4. 文档管理 ==

Admin -> Browser: 设置文档可见性
Browser -> Ctrl: PUT /api/v1/admin/documents/{fileMd5}/visibility\n{isPublic: true|false}
Ctrl -> DocSvc: updateDocumentVisibility(fileMd5, isPublic)
DocSvc -> DB: UPDATE file_upload SET is_public = ?
DocSvc -> Ext: ES 索引更新 isPublic 字段
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}

Admin -> Browser: 编辑文档组织标签
Browser -> Ctrl: PUT /api/v1/admin/documents/{fileMd5}/org-tag\n{orgTag: "tagId"}
Ctrl -> DocSvc: updateDocumentOrgTag(fileMd5, orgTag)
DocSvc -> DB: UPDATE file_upload SET org_tag = ?
DocSvc -> Ext: ES 索引更新 orgTag 字段
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}

Admin -> Browser: 重试向量化
Browser -> Ctrl: POST /api/v1/documents/{fileMd5}/vectorization/retry
Ctrl -> DocSvc: enqueueAsyncVectorizationRetry(fileMd5, userId)
DocSvc -> Kafka: 发送 FileProcessingTask
Kafka -> Kafka: FileProcessingConsumer\n异步下载 → 重新切分 → 重新向量化
DocSvc --> Ctrl: {code:200, data:{vectorizationStatus:"PENDING"}}

Admin -> Browser: 删除 / 重索引文档
Browser -> Ctrl: DELETE /api/v1/documents/{fileMd5}\n或 POST /api/v1/documents/{fileMd5}/reindex
Ctrl -> DocSvc: deleteDocument / reindexDocument
DocSvc -> Ext: ES 删除索引 / 重建\nMinIO 删除文件 / 保留
DocSvc -> DB: 删除 document_vectors\n/ chunk_info / file_upload 记录
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200}
Browser --> Admin: 操作完成

== 5. 对话历史查看 ==

Admin -> Browser: 进入对话历史页面 (/chat-history)
Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/admin/conversation\n?userid=&start_date=&end_date=
Ctrl -> ConvSvc: getAllConversations\n(adminUsername, targetUsername, startDate, endDate)
ConvSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM conversations\n(含日期范围 + 用户过滤)
DB --> ConvSvc: 对话记录 (username, question,\nanswer, referenceMappingsJson)
ConvSvc --> Ctrl: 全量对话列表
Ctrl --> Browser: {code:200, data:[...]}
Browser --> Admin: 展示: 可按 username,\nconversationId, 日期范围筛选\n含引用来源映射

@enduml
